### Get All Doctors
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctors?
    page=0&
    size=10&
    sortField=name

### Get Doctor by ID
GET {{host}}/api/doctors/1

### Get Doctor by ID - Not Found
GET {{host}}/api/doctors/999

### POST Create Doctor
POST {{host}}/api/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dr. John Smith",
  "specialisation": "Cardiology",
  "email": "john.smith@hospital.com"
}

### PUT Update Doctor
PUT {{host}}/api/doctors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dr. John Smith Updated",
  "specialisation": "Neurology",
  "email": "john.updated@hospital.com"
}

### PATCH Partial Update - Name Only
PATCH {{host}}/api/doctors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dr. John Patched"
}

### DELETE Doctor
DELETE {{host}}/api/doctors/10

### DELETE Doctor - Not Found
DELETE {{host}}/api/doctors/999

### FILTER - By Name and Specialisation
GET {{host}}/api/doctors/filter?name=john&specialisation=cardio

### FILTER - By Department with Pagination
GET {{host}}/api/doctors/filter?departmentName=neurology&page=0&size=5&sort=name,asc